DAAD Reborn Compiler (DRC) is a replacement of DAAD compiler (DC), running in modern OS (Windows, Linux MacOS).

It also included a modern replacement of MCRF for Amstrad CPC, and DAADMAKER, a tool to build DAAD tapes and disks for ZX Spectrum.

Please find usage and build instructions, download links in the DRC Wiki: https://github.com/daad-adventure-writer/DRC/wiki

Download at

http://www.ngpaws.com/downloads/DAAD/DRC/



